high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the end of the windows on your right, turn left and go to the laptop on the coffee table to your left.
Close and pick up the laptop between the two vase's, on the coffee table.
Turn to your left and walk back to the windows, then go straight across the room to the white end table.
Place the laptop on the right side of the statue, on the white end table.
anns.task_desc: Put the laptop on the end table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn left again and walk over to the side of the coffee table.
Close the lid of the laptop that is on the coffee table and pick it up.
Turn left and walk over to the window, then turn right and walk over to the white table with the statue on it.
Put the closed laptop on top of the white table to the right of the statue.
anns.task_desc: Put a closed laptop on a white table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk between the gray couch and the white coffee table.
Pick up the gray laptop on the white coffee table.
Walk right between the white coffee table at the wall to the long white table across the room.
Put the laptop on the long white table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the laptop and put it on the long white table.
